752
00:50:46,000 --> 00:50:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači 880 eura, nešto manje, manje od 1000 eura.

753
00:50:51,000 --> 00:50:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači 980 eura, all inclusive, 7 dana Hurgada.

754
00:50:54,000 --> 00:50:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] To su je top hoteli, oma do mora, do plaže.

755
00:50:57,000 --> 00:51:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam bio tamo, to dosta lijepo izgleda.

756
00:51:01,000 --> 00:51:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo novac vrijedi poprilično.

757
00:51:03,000 --> 00:51:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nas je 8 bilo, jeli smo 8 steakova, platio sam 70 eura.

758
00:51:06,000 --> 00:51:10,000
